you out to dinner tonight.
我们想邀请你和我们一起共进晚餐

101
00:06:28,890 --> 00:06:32,570
To celebrate your "30 under
30" thing. Right,Sheldon?
为了庆祝你的"3030" 没错吧 Sheldon?

102
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,250
