Peoplemagazine photo shoot...
我立马被接去拍封面照

139
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,710
Have any of you boys ever
been to a photo shoot?
你们几个拍过杂志封面照么?

140
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,550
No.
没

141
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:41,600
