00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:53,750
Our new friend is going to be Iron Man.
我们的新朋友是 钢铁侠

291
00:17:56,320 --> 00:18:00,100
I can go all night...
我一晚上都能...

292
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:04,330
Welcome to the Raj Mahal.
欢迎来到"Raj陵" (引自"泰姬陵")

293
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:06,210
It's very nice. Good night,Raj.
很不错的地方 晚安 Raj

294
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:08,080
- No,no,Wait. The evening's not over.
- Yes,it is.
- 不 不 等等 夜生活还没结束呢
- 结束了啊

295
00:18:08,090 --> 00:18:12,110
No,it's time to put on
some R. Kelly and suck face.
现在得听听R. Kelly 再一起吸吸脸哟

296
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:17,010
- Oh,wow,is the evening over?
- Wait,wait,wait!
- 噢 喔哦 夜生活结束了吗?
- 等等 等等 等等!

297
00:18:17,020 --> 00:18:19,220
That's my mommy and
daddy calling from India.
是我爸妈从印度打来

298
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:20,850
I want you to meet my parents.
我想让你见见我父母

299
00:18:20,870 --> 00:18:23,020
Wait. Meet them?
等等 见他们?

300
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:29,750
Hello,Mommy,Daddy. Good to see
you. How are you? I'm not drunk.
好啊 爸爸妈妈 很高兴见到你们
你们好吗? 我没有喝醉哦

301
00:18:30,420 --> 00:18:33,540
- Why would you say that?
- Just making conversation.
- 干嘛这么说?
- 随便说说而已

302
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:36,810
Mommy,Daddy,I want you to
meet my new squeeze,Penny.
爸爸妈妈  我想让你见见我的新女友 Penny

303
00:18:36,820 --> 00:18:39,990
I'm not your squeeze.
There is no squeezing.
我不是你的女友 他没有什么女友

304
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:42,650
I can't see her.
Center her in the frame.
我看不到她 镜头对准她

305
00:18:42,660 --> 00:18:44,810
Here you go. Cute,huh?
看看吧 漂亮哈?

306
00:18:45,580 --> 00:18:47,680
She's not Indian.
她不是印度人

307
00:18:47,690 --> 00:18:50,260
So she's not Indian. The boy
is just sowing some wild oats.
不是印度人又怎样
咱儿子还年轻 放荡放荡嘛

308
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:54,200
No,no,no,there's no sowing,no
squeezing and no sucking face.
没有没有 没有放荡
我也不是啥女友 咱也没吸脸

309
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:56,550
What if he gets her pregnant?
万一他把她肚子搞大了怎么办?

310
00:18:56,570 --> 00:19:00,580
Is this little hotsy-totsy who you want
as the mother of your grandchildren?
你想要这个粉嫩小妞做你孙辈的母亲?

311
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:02,900
What right do you have to pick
with whom I can have children with?
你们有什么权利选择我跟谁生孩子?

312
00:19:02,930 --> 00:19:05,660
Look,Rajesh,I understand
you're in America.
听着 Rajesh 我知道你在美国

313
00:19:05,690 --> 00:19:08,380
You want to try the "local cuisine."
想尝尝"当地小吃"

314
00:19:08,390 --> 00:19:12,480
Trust me. You don't want
it for a steady diet.
但是相信我 那玩意儿吃不久的

315
00:19:12,970 --> 00:19:13,970
Now you listen to me.
你们听我说

316
00:19:13,980 --> 00:19:17,420
I am no longer a child and I
will not be spoken to like one.
我已经不是小孩子了 说话也不会再像小孩子

317
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:20,720
Now if you'll excuse
me,I have to go throw up.
失陪失陪 我去吐一吐

318
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,860
What's wrong with him?
他怎么了?

319
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:27,500
I don't know. Maybe
it's the local cuisine.
我不知道 可能是吃了当地小吃

320
00:19:31,790 --> 00:19:35,710
Okay,well,it's nice to meet you.
好吧 那么 很高兴见到你们

321
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:38,840
I'm just gonna set
you on down over here.
我就把你们放在桌上吧

322
00:19:38,860 --> 00:19:42,150
And I'm gonna leave,so namaste.
我要走了 Namaste (合十礼 印度见面拜礼)

323
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:49,130
And FYI,you'd be lucky to
have me as a daughter-in-law.
还有告诉你们 我做他媳妇 是你们的福气

324
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:54,690
She's feisty. I like that.
妞有点脾气嘛 我喜欢

325
00:20:04,450 --> 00:20:06,800
Raj,what are you doing?
Raj 你在干嘛?

326
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:13,460
No,no notes. If you have
something to say to me,say it.
不 不用纸条 如果你有话要说 说出来

327
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,770
Sorry.
对不起

328
00:20:30,420 --> 00:20:34,120
Oh,sweetie,it's okay.
噢 宝贝 没关系拉

